00:40:17,990 --> 00:40:19,920
in the position of Prime Minister.

853
00:40:20,990 --> 00:40:21,910
I'm afraid

854
00:40:23,870 --> 00:40:25,870
someone will compete with me for it.

855
00:40:30,750 --> 00:40:32,180
Since Your Majesty ascended the throne,

856
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:33,410
the power of the Princess

857
00:40:33,410 --> 00:40:34,870
has not only not been reduced

858
00:40:34,870 --> 00:40:36,530
but has become even stronger.

859
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:37,390
Taishang Huang

860
00:40:37,390 --> 00:40:40,120
often receives court officials in the Taiji Hall

861
00:40:40,460 --> 00:40:42,990
and discusses everything with the Princess.

862
00:40:44,350 --> 00:40:46,020
What do you mean by this?

863
00:40:46,950 --> 00:40:48,910
Forgive my boldness, Your Majesty.

864
00:40:48,910 --> 00:40:51,510
If Your Majesty wishes to create a prosperous era,

865
00:40:51,510 --> 00:40:52,710
there are some things

866
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:55,000
that need to be prepared in advance.

867
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:58,190
Lu Tong,

868
00:40:59,510 --> 00:41:01,310
you have always been cautious.

869
00:41:02,630 --> 00:41:05,160
It is precisely because I am a cautious person

870
00:41:05,320 --> 00:41:08,180
that I advise Your Majesty to make a decision early.

871
00:41:08,550 --> 00:41:10,410
Otherwise, the Princess' Palace

872
00:41:10,430 --> 00:41:12,430
will surely stir up shocking waves.

873
00:41:14,750 --> 00:41:16,010
You are exaggerating.

874
00:41:18,080 --> 00:41:20,360
Have the gifts for the four armies at the North Gate,

875
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:22,750
especially the gifts for the Left and Right Cavalries,

876
00:41:22,750 --> 00:41:23,950
been sent this month?

877
00:41:24,270 --> 00:41:25,630
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

878
00:41:25,630 --> 00:41:27,960
All the prepared gifts have been sent out.

879
00:41:28,070 --> 00:41:29,130
Keep sending them.

880
00:41:29,270 --> 00:41:30,600
Take all the good things

881
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:32,250
from the Eastern Palace

882
00:41:32,250 --> 00:41:33,310
and give them away.

883
00:41:33,830 --> 00:41:34,760
Don't hold back.

884
00:41:35,270 --> 00:41:35,670
Yes,

885
00:41:35,870 --> 00:41:36,670
Your Majesty.

886
00:41:58,950 --> 00:42:00,830
From the seventh rank to the fourth rank,

887
00:42:00,830 --> 00:42:02,760
five people were promoted at once.

888
00:42:02,950 --> 00:42:03,550
Princess,

889
00:42:03,910 --> 00:42:05,190
you must intervene.

890
00:42:05,350 --> 00:42:07,810
You can't let His Majesty succeed so easily.

891
00:42:08,270 --> 00:42:09,070
Don't bother.

892
00:42:12,390 --> 00:42:13,390
How many more days

893
00:42:13,550 --> 00:42:15,610
until Lu Lingfeng reaches Chang'an?

894
00:42:15,960 --> 00:42:17,390
According to my subordinate's report,

895
00:42:17,390 --> 00:42:19,310
he has already arrived at Fengtian County.

896
00:42:19,310 --> 00:42:21,370
He should arrive in the next few days.

897
00:42:23,230 --> 00:42:24,950
I just don't know why His Majesty

898
00:42:24,950 --> 00:42:27,110
used the excuse of escorting the golden peaches

899
00:42:27,110 --> 00:42:29,070
to summon Lu Lingfeng

900
00:42:30,790 --> 00:42:31,920
back to the capital.

901
00:42:32,470 --> 00:42:33,310
Who cares?

902
00:42:35,430 --> 00:42:36,830
I miss Lu Lingfeng.

903
00:42:37,800 --> 00:42:40,670
Isn't His Majesty doing us a favor?

904
00:42:42,590 --> 00:42:43,190
Princess,

905
00:42:43,510 --> 00:42:44,510
many people heard

906
00:42:44,780 --> 00:42:46,310
when he called out "Mother"

907
00:42:46,790 --> 00:42:48,310
at Chengfo Temple.

908
00:42:49,830 --> 00:42:50,910
So what?

909
00:42:51,780 --> 00:42:53,920
I have never deliberately hidden

910
00:42:53,950 --> 00:42:55,880
my relationship with Lu Lingfeng.

911
00:42:56,100 --> 00:42:56,910
Cen Zhi,

912
00:42:59,150 --> 00:43:01,350
who do you think

913
00:43:02,390 --> 00:43:04,150
Chang'an belongs to now?

914
00:43:04,500 --> 00:43:06,040
Of course it's yours, Princess.

915
00:43:06,040 --> 00:43:12,480
[Jinguang Gate]

916
00:43:06,910 --> 00:43:07,630
Chang'an

917
00:43:09,030 --> 00:43:11,190
will always be at your feet.

918
00:43:13,030 --> 00:43:14,350
I fear it will rain

919
00:43:16,590 --> 00:43:19,290
in Chang'an again.

920
00:43:29,650 --> 00:43:35,210
[Resolutely heading west with a risky return]
[In the autumn of Chang'an, a storm is coming]
